# Hero Sections Module Guide

## Public Endpoints
### Get Hero Sections
- `GET /api/hero-sections/{placement_identifier}`
- Returns active hero sections for specific placement
- Ordered by `order_column`

## Admin Endpoints
### Manage Hero Sections
- List all: `GET /api/admin/hero-sections`
- Create: `POST /api/admin/hero-sections`
- Update: `PUT/PATCH /api/admin/hero-sections/{id}`
- Delete: `DELETE /api/admin/hero-sections/{id}`

### Hero Section Fields
- `placement_identifier`: Section placement (e.g., 'home_page_main')
- `title`: Section title
- `subtitle`: Section subtitle
- `cta_text`: Call-to-action text
- `cta_link`: Call-to-action link
- `image_url_desktop`: Desktop image URL
- `image_url_mobile`: Mobile image URL
- `video_url`: Video URL (optional)
- `text_alignment`: Text alignment ('left', 'center', 'right')
- `order_column`: Sorting order
- `is_active`: Active status
- `active_period_start`: Start date of active period
- `active_period_end`: End date of active period

